column17: Genus changed in 2016 - Taxonomy still uncertain
Year 2010: all Porites are pooled for the following sites and habitats: LTER 1 (Fringe, 10m, 17m), LTER 2-6 (10m, 17m)
Year 2010: P. irregularis, P. rus, and Porites spp. Massive are the only Porites spp. found at LTER 2-6 (Fringe); Sum these 3 categories for total Porites spp. for all years except 2010.
